{"tid":1324370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新自由主義其實都係敵人","createTime":"2019-07-16T14:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T05:31:32.000Z","uid":266924,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b0aca41564103720a18a824f0fe16cf3e2790d0e","tid":1324370,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:06:49.000Z","msg":"呢班人最唔想有普選，因為民治嘅社會係呢班無皇管嘅商家頭號敵人<br />\n正因為無皇管，所以一直以來壓搾平民，令香港人成為商家嘅奴隸。呢班人配合政府，媒體，不斷提高樓價，甚至危害有本土特色嘅小店<br />\n今次沙田一事就見到當中涉及嘅利害關係<br />\n警察一早有圍堵示威者意圖，新鴻基嘅做法完全配合政權清場。<span style=\"color: red;\">商家咁做必然為咗利益，就係避免普選發生。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當有普選，就意味住新自由主義嘅終結。商家唔可以從中取得最大利益，有民治為基礎下，新自由主義定必迎向終結。</span>"},{"pid":"ff772fd24c9c2a1f9c8287818ec81fbccfc74ad5","tid":1324370,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9180f6779e47012754c385b6a0ac8618bbc52bdb","tid":1324370,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02403f0a4e0ff87007abadbb31e91906c73c4b25","tid":1324370,"uid":144109,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"萬惡新主由主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔明可以睇下許寶強老師既書的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4036b7f6e5c8cf94c7f1abfee8f992a25cc46d3","tid":1324370,"uid":266924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:10:07.000Z","msg":"所以屌鳩新鴻基係非常正確<br />\n香港人要認清敵人，先會邁向民主同和平"},{"pid":"01dcb45eece5af882ab7e3887b8404d92c5ea7e3","tid":1324370,"uid":120911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"你講緊香港？<br />\n依家係威權資本主義喎<br />\n紅色霸權加地產霸權雙重夾擊"},{"pid":"481923d2c3f88da41decb5b892ff31600999ddb6","tid":1324370,"uid":115279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n亦因為咁香港無咩大型罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla