":"同意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係...<br />\n<br />\n1. 中共係主要敵人，新自由主義係次要敵人。現階段應該先團結次要敵人。<br />\n<br />\n2. 熱狗d友不學無術，明明係右翼又學人講新自由主義批判，笑死人。99%運動留返比我地左翼得架啦。"},{"pid":"30020d231345357be0503c8569ea07ab66c6dfc9","tid":1324370,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d9d86402ab13754813d19ce58003648399fd4f","tid":1324370,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:13:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"羅永生稱依種狀態為「虛擬自由主義」"},{"pid":"3db3e3c1e0c703ce6fac744b9df0a345635a454f","tid":1324370,"uid":30138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"07e409ff66fc58a73ac56ba6f8c20f953996a09c","tid":1324370,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"推多一次唔推了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f6b2a9915c98b46b5feba53a6b434a5d4cc92d","tid":1324370,"uid":212624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"所以我地係崇尚古典自由主義？"}]}